#19022
Entrance to the beatiful village, Gdangus~
Hidden beneath the forest trees, this unnoticable village strikes you
with great awe. Multi-colored cobblestone lines your path in all directions.
A large adamantite arch greets your entrance. Small quaint stores are in
perfect condition lining the route in all directions.  A mass of people
travel in and out each day causing the cobblestone to be dull and worn out.
A town crier rests high up on a platform to your north calling out village
information. A noose and hanging stage appears close in distance, symbolizing
that this small village won't put up with any unlawful citizens.
~
